{"tid":2234883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國國防委員會：已證華為與共產黨有連繫 須提早於2025年全面移除華為設備","createTime":"2020-10-08T08:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T12:18:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":184,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1a19a51f352b6a7458aa927aceec5e4016438c","tid":2234883,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"英國防委員會：華為與中國政府勾連2025年移除設備<br />\n<br />\n英國國會國防委員會指，有明確證據證明中國電訊設備製造商華為與中國政府有勾連，英國須提早兩年，在2025年將華為設備全部移除出英國5G網絡，委員會又強調，西方急需團結，制衡中國的技術優勢。<br />\n<br />\n英國年初容許華為有限度參與當地5G網絡建設，但首相約翰遜在美國壓力，7月決定不選用華為5G設備，並會在2027年從基礎建設中全面移除華為裝置。美國及盟友一直指控北京利用華為設備進行竊取資訊等間諜活動，存在重大安全風險， 華為多次否認有關指控。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360698\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2360698&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5OgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=2cee5128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2360698</a>"},{"pid":"4010647b48319570a52accc6b2403b1f35ba79df","tid":2234883,"uid":182715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37dca5b231c84bbec536ec9973fef19a05588ba","tid":2234883,"uid":28397,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"重要等到2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79352d1b817712304f60e9f5c97a84f257b085a9","tid":2234883,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"